0:00:00.000,0:00:03.860
Kune mukoma uko, iwe une mudzimai mutsva.

0:00:03.860,0:00:07.240
Iwe unoda mukadzi wako - mudzimai ane mutsa -

0:00:07.240,0:00:13.200
asi mukukanganisa, iwe wakazviwana uchiroora umwe munhu kunze

0:00:13.200,0:00:19.800
uye iwe wakarenda nzvimbo yakavanda - imba inemupanda wekurara kune imwe nzvimbo.

0:00:19.800,0:00:24.500
Iwe zvino watanga kuronga nguva yako - dzimwe nguva iwe unorara apa, imwe nguva, ikoko.

0:00:24.500,0:00:29.580
Tiri kungokuudza - gore riri kuuya, haugoni kuramba uchizviita.

0:00:29.580,0:00:32.000
Zvichava nengozi kwauri.

0:00:32.000,0:00:34.480
Buda uuye kudzikinuro yako.

0:00:34.480,0:00:37.940
Mukoma wandiri kutaura nezvake, ndapota budai.

0:00:37.940,0:00:41.820
Mukusimbisa huporofita, murume anobva mu korokodzano

0:00:41.820,0:00:44.900
uye anofamba kuenda kune mu Porofita T.B. Joshua.

0:00:44.900,0:00:46.800
Iwe hausi muduku kwazvo here?

0:00:46.800,0:00:47.840
Hongu, Munhu wa Mwari.

0:00:47.840,0:00:49.840
Ini ndavhiringidzika.

0:00:49.840,0:00:50.880
Wakavhiringidzika?

0:00:50.880,0:00:51.940
Hongu, Munhu wa Mwari.

0:00:51.940,0:00:52.840
Wakavhiringidzika?

0:00:52.840,0:00:53.680
Hongu, Munhu wa Mwari.

0:00:53.680,0:00:55.860
Asi iyi haina kumbovhiringidzika!

0:00:55.860,0:00:59.820
Nguva ye Uprofita

0:00:59.820,0:01:03.340
Kana iwe uchivhiringidzika, iyi haizombofi yakavhiringidzika.

0:01:03.340,0:01:08.100
Ati, "Ndakavhiringidzika.

0:01:08.100,0:01:11.360
Kana iwe uchivhiringidzika, nzvimbo iyoyo inovhiringidzika here?

0:01:11.360,0:01:12.660
Handisi kukunzwa.

0:01:12.660,0:01:14.140
[Aihwa!]

0:01:14.140,0:01:20.780
Ndiye akavhiringidzika asi nzvimbo iyoyo inzvimbo yakasiyana.

0:01:20.780,0:01:29.240
Inzwa gore rinotevera, zvauri kuita muchivande iko zvino - kana ukazviedza gore rinouya, iwe uchafa.

0:01:29.240,0:01:36.960
Nemhaka yokuti mukadzi wawakaisa munzvimbo iyoyo, vari kukutsvaka uye vachakuwana.

0:01:36.960,0:01:40.100
Mangwanani-ngwanani, vachawana kuti vakuuraya pane imwe nzvimbo.

0:01:40.100,0:01:44.840
Saka, nenguva yaunoenda kune umwe, iwe uchaziva kuti wavhiringidzika.

0:01:44.840,0:01:50.600
Iye murume wechidiki. Iwe wakanaka kwazvo; Ndapota usarega nyika ino ichikunyengera.

0:01:50.600,0:01:52.620
Zvakanaka? Saka, ndinoda kukuona.

0:01:52.620,0:01:54.720
Ndinokutendai, Munhu wa Mwari.

0:01:54.720,0:01:58.800
Ko mudzimai wako chaiye akaitei kwauri?

0:01:58.800,0:02:01.320
Hapana, Munhu wa Mwari.

0:02:01.320,0:02:03.840
Ndichamudana.

0:02:03.840,0:02:05.700
Une makore mangani?

0:02:05.700,0:02:07.700
Makumi matatu nematanhatu.

0:02:07.700,0:02:09.400
Zvakanaka, ndimirire.

0:02:09.400,0:02:11.900
Mumwe wacho, ndichamukoka.

0:02:11.900,0:02:16.080
Tichanyengetera naye uye tichamuratidza budiriro ye ramangwana rake

0:02:16.080,0:02:18.080
uye ini ndichati, 'Ndapota, siya munun'una wangu'.

0:02:18.080,0:02:23.980
Zvose zvatiri kutaura nezvekuti, siya munun'una wangu.

0:02:23.980,0:02:30.660
Nguva ye Huporofita

0:02:30.660,0:02:35.820
Mukadzi wacho haana kuvhiringidzika; murume uyu akavhiringidzika.

0:02:35.820,0:02:39.120
Saka, uyo asina kuvhiringidzika anofanira kukwanisa kuudza uyo akavhiringidzika,

0:02:39.120,0:02:41.740
"Ndapota, dzokera kwauri kubva".

0:02:43.020,0:02:47.400
NHUNGAMIRO YE HUPENYU

0:02:47.400,0:02:48.720
Svondo yemusi we Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:02:48.720,0:02:54.480
Idzi ndidzo nyaya dzausingazo kumbira munhu wa Mwari kuti akunyengeterere.

0:02:54.480,0:03:00.260
Iwe uchasiya nyaya inokosha - iwe unenge uchiudza munhu wa Mwari chimwe chinhu chakasiyana.

0:03:00.260,0:03:03.800
Ichi ndicho chikonzero tiri pano. Chero chipi nechipi chinogona kuva nengozi kwauri

0:03:03.800,0:03:08.280
iwe unoda Jesu kuti auye uye akuparadzanise nazvo.

0:03:08.280,0:03:12.140
Ndakati anofanira kuuya nomudzimai ari kumba

0:03:12.140,0:03:17.560
uye mudzimai kumba angave achizvinzwa izvi kekutanga.

0:03:17.560,0:03:21.360
Zita rangu ndi Mr Emmanuel.

0:03:21.360,0:03:23.860
Ini ndinobva ku Togo.

0:03:23.860,0:03:29.140
Mukadzi ari pedyo neni ndiye mudzimai wangu, wandakachata naye.

0:03:29.140,0:03:35.280
Munguva yehuporofita hwe svondo yemusi Mugovera, munhu wa Mwari akaporofita

0:03:35.280,0:03:38.540
kuti paiva nomurume we chidiki pano uyo akanga akaroora

0:03:38.540,0:03:43.480
asi akanga achirenda imba mu chivande kune umwe mukadzi kunze.

0:03:43.480,0:03:49.480
Pakarepo pandakanzwa, zvakandiomera kuti ndibude.

0:03:49.480,0:03:53.640
Ndakanga ndakamirira kuti ndione kana mumwe munhu aizobuda.

0:03:53.640,0:04:00.660
Pakarepo, ndakanzwa sokuti kwaiva nemuchina waizunguzika zunguzika mukati mangu.

0:04:00.660,0:04:06.060
Muviri wangu wakanga usingagoni kudzoreka zvakare; zvinhu zvose zvakanga zvichi zunguzwa zvakanyanya.

0:04:06.060,0:04:07.900
Wanzwa zvaataura here?

0:04:07.900,0:04:14.160
Ati pandakanga ndichitaura, akanga achitsvaka mumwe munhu kuti abude.

0:04:14.160,0:04:17.000
Asi asati apedza kutarisa kumativi echechi -

0:04:17.000,0:04:22.120
akatarisa kune rumwe rutivi rwechechi asi asati atarisa shure,

0:04:22.120,0:04:24.580
chimwe chinhu chakarova mwoyo wake.

0:04:24.580,0:04:26.920
Unoziva kuti Jesu anokuda.

0:04:26.920,0:04:29.060
Ane nzira yekukutora iwe.

0:04:29.060,0:04:31.300
Ndinoreva kuti, Iye ndiye Musiki wako.

0:04:31.300,0:04:34.520
Ati akange asingakwanisi kufema zvakare.

0:04:34.520,0:04:37.040
Aifanira kukurumidza kubuda.

0:04:37.040,0:04:40.520
Ndakatarisa-tarisa asi handina kuona ani zvake achibuda.

0:04:40.520,0:04:48.540
Panguva iyo muviri wangu wakatanga kudedera, ndakatanga kunzwa, "Rongedza zvinhu zvako utize".

0:04:48.540,0:04:52.360
Handizivi kuti ndakasvika sei pamberi peatari.

0:04:52.360,0:04:56.420
Zvose zvakataurwa nemunhu wa Mwari ndezve chokwadi - zana kubva mu zana pachokwadi.

0:04:56.420,0:05:01.980
Mumwe mukadzi akasumwa kwandiri neshamwari yaipa jecha kwatiri.

0:05:01.980,0:05:04.500
Akanga aine vana vatanhatu kare.

0:05:04.500,0:05:06.960
Ndakanga ndichivabatsira.

0:05:06.960,0:05:14.420
Rimwe zuva, pandakanga ndichivabatsira akakurukura neni,

0:05:14.420,0:05:19.060
aida kuva nemwana neni  kuitira kuti pangove nekubatana pakati pedu

0:05:19.060,0:05:22.360
kunyangwe pandakabuda munyika.

0:05:22.360,0:05:26.400
Ndakamuudza kuti kana tikadaro, zvinogona kukonzera dambudziko kwandiri

0:05:26.400,0:05:28.700
nokuti ndakanga ndiri mutorwa munyika.

0:05:28.700,0:05:32.060
Akati ini ndinofanira kuziva nzira yekugadzirisa nyaya yacho.

0:05:32.060,0:05:38.660
Pakupedzisira, ndakatanga kuva nehukama naye.

0:05:38.660,0:05:43.200
Akabva ava nepamuviri uye ndokubereka mwana wangu.

0:05:43.200,0:05:45.540
Mudzimai wangu haazive chinhu chezvandiri kutaura iye zvino.

0:05:45.540,0:05:48.260
Ino ndiyo nguva yake yekutanga kunzwa zvinhu zvose izvi.

0:05:48.260,0:05:51.100
Saka, ino ndiyo nguva yokutanga apo mudzimai wako ari kunzwa izvi kubva kwauri?

0:05:51.100,0:05:53.520
Hongu, Munhu wa Mwari.

0:05:53.520,0:06:00.320
Akanga achindifungidzira asi ini ndakanga ndisingakwanisi kutaura chinhu kwaari.

0:06:00.320,0:06:05.080
Mukadzi iyeye akashandisa mwana uyu kundityisidzira.

0:06:05.080,0:06:07.080
Pose paaibvunza chimwe chinhu

0:06:07.080,0:06:11.080
kana kuti akandikumbira kuti ndiuye kumba kwake, izvo zvandakanga ndisingadi kuita,

0:06:11.080,0:06:16.600
iye aiti aizotakura mwana wake - mwana wangu, aizomusiya pamba pangu.

0:06:16.600,0:06:18.920
Mukadzi wacho ishamwari yemhuri

0:06:18.920,0:06:23.640
asi ini ndakanga ndisingadi chinhu chaigona kukonzera dambudziko pakati pangu nemudzimai wangu.

0:06:23.640,0:06:29.700
Mudzimai wangu aimutora se mukoma wake uye aigara achimugadzira vhudzi rake.

0:06:29.700,0:06:36.140
Panguva yemuchato wedu, aive nesu uye akatibatsira nezvose zvatakanga tichiita.

0:06:36.140,0:06:39.340
Mudzimai wangu akafunga kuti aive hanzvadzi yangu.

0:06:39.340,0:06:43.380
Zvakanaka. Madhamu, makadii?

0:06:43.380,0:06:47.200
Iwe unofanira kuvonga Mwari; haufaniri kushungurudzwa.

0:06:47.200,0:06:51.320
Ino ndiyo nguva zvino iyo Mwari anoda kusimbisa wanano iyi.

0:06:51.320,0:06:56.360
Kana pasina kuroorana pakati pako naye, ndingadai ndakuudza.

0:06:56.360,0:07:02.000
Ndinoona hukama uhu huchibva kuna Mwari; uyu muchato unobva kuna Mwari.

0:07:02.000,0:07:09.440
Hazvinei nenyaya yacho, sekutaura kwe Mupositori Pauro, "Chii chingagone kundiparadzanisa kubva murudo rwa Kristu".

0:07:09.440,0:07:16.500
Chero zvakaitika, usanetseka.

0:07:16.500,0:07:19.140
Saka, kuti iwe uzive kuti haana kukodzera.

0:07:19.140,0:07:21.020
Unoziva here mukadzi waari kutaura nezvake?

0:07:21.020,0:07:23.360
Hongu

0:07:23.360,0:07:31.120
Ndinoziva mukadzi wacho; akaita se mukoma wangu, shamwari ye mhuri kwandiri

0:07:31.120,0:07:39.500
Munguva yemuchato wedu, iye akaronga chimwe chikwata che shamwari.

0:07:39.500,0:07:42.440
uye akaronga komiti yake ye shamwari pachake

0:07:42.440,0:07:45.980
nokuti takange tine hukama hwe pedyo naye.

0:07:45.980,0:07:49.700
Anoita se mukoma uye shamwari yemhuri kwatiri.

0:07:49.700,0:07:54.400
Ane vana vatanhatu kare.

0:07:54.400,0:07:57.980
Wechinomwe - ndakafunga kuti aiva mwanakomana wemukadzi wacho.

0:07:57.980,0:08:02.980
Ndakanga ndisingazivi kuti wechinomwe ndiye mwanakomana wemurume wangu.

0:08:02.980,0:08:07.080
Ndiri pano; Ndakavhiringidzika uye handizivi zvokuita.

0:08:07.080,0:08:08.680
Ndapota.

0:08:08.680,0:08:11.020
Uri kuzvinzwa kekutanga izvozvi here?

0:08:11.020,0:08:14.080
Hongu, ino ndiyo nguva yangu yokutanga kunzwa izvi.

0:08:14.080,0:08:16.080
Zvakanaka, patsvene.

0:08:16.080,0:08:18.020
Ndinofunga kuti mukadzi wacho aripo?

0:08:18.020,0:08:20.740
Hongu, Munhu wa Mwari.

0:08:20.740,0:08:27.680
Nemhaka yokuti iye ... Madhamu, sei uri kufemereka?

0:08:27.680,0:08:29.020
Zvakanaka.

0:08:29.020,0:08:34.620
Saka, ndini ndati vanofanira kuudza mukadzi wacho.

0:08:34.620,0:08:38.600
Haana kumboziva kuti iwe uchange uri pano; haana kumboziva kuti zvaizoita seizvi.

0:08:38.600,0:08:43.120
Pamwe, zvichida akafunga kuti ndinoda kusimbisa imba yavo.

0:08:43.120,0:08:45.120
Zvakanaka, patsvene.

0:08:45.120,0:08:49.440
Madhamu, musanetseka. Mushure mebasa, ndinofanira kuona mhuri.

0:08:49.440,0:08:54.540
Asi zviri nyore, vatariri - zvandinoda kuvaonera zviri nyore.

0:08:54.540,0:08:57.940
Svondo inotevera, vachauya kuzopa uchapupu.

0:08:57.940,0:08:59.560
Uyu ndiye mudzimai wako.

0:08:59.560,0:09:01.360
Nhaika?

0:09:01.360,0:09:02.860
Ndicha....

0:09:02.860,0:09:16.540
Uchapupu hwe uporofita hwa Baba na Mai Emmanuel

0:09:16.540,0:09:18.760
Ndapota ndiregererei.

0:09:18.760,0:09:20.400
Zvakanaka, patsvene.

0:09:20.400,0:09:25.200
Saka, ndichasangana nemumwe mukadzi, ndichataura naye.

0:09:25.200,0:09:27.460
Asi chimwe chinhu chakajeka.

0:09:27.460,0:09:31.460
Mwana iyeye mwana wemhuri iyi.

0:09:31.460,0:09:34.500
Iwe haugoni kumuramba; mwana wemurume wako.

0:09:34.500,0:09:41.560
Asi iye achasiya wanano yako uye Mwari acharegerera murume wako ne kuregerera mukadzi iyeye.

0:09:41.560,0:09:44.600
Mwana wacho ndewe mhuri iyi. Nhaika.

0:09:44.600,0:09:49.120
Asi ini ndinoda kukuvimbisai, wanano iyi ndeyako.

0:09:49.120,0:09:53.540
Ndichakuratidza chikonzero nei iwe usingakwanisi kusiya imba.

0:09:53.540,0:09:57.880
Iwe uchatanga kufadzwa ne muchato uyu kubva ikozvino.

0:09:57.880,0:10:00.040
Ndizvoka? Ini ndichasangana nemi vanhu imi.

0:10:00.040,0:10:01.740
Saka, mukadzi wacho anofanira kumirira.

0:10:01.740,0:10:05.800
Ndatenda. Vavhangeri vachasangana nemukadzi wacho, vachimufadza

0:10:05.800,0:10:09.200
nekumupa nzvimbo yekugara. Haafaniri kutiza.

0:10:09.200,0:10:10.840
Madhamu, ndipei ruoko rwako.

0:10:10.840,0:10:13.020
Wanzwa zvandataura hee?

0:10:13.020,0:10:15.120
Zvakanaka, patsvene. Ndichakuona.

0:10:15.120,0:10:17.020
Zvakanaka, enda unondimirira.

0:10:17.020,0:10:19.420
Uchapupu hwe uporofita hwa Baba na Mai Emmanuel

0:10:19.420,0:10:24.480
Svondo ye musi we Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:10:24.480,0:10:28.560
Ndinoziva hazvirevi chinhu kune vazhinji vedu pano.

0:10:28.560,0:10:34.640
Vamwe vangangoseka uko vachiti, "A, honai wo!"

0:10:34.640,0:10:41.900
Zuva iro Mwari achabata iwe, iwe uchaziva kuti zvinoreva zvakawanda!

0:10:41.900,0:10:50.300
Vamwe vanoti, "Hehe! Hapana chinetso".

0:10:50.300,0:10:53.900
Zuva iro Mwari achabata iwe!

0:10:53.900,0:10:55.900
Zvakanaka. Saka, ndinokutendai.

0:10:55.900,0:10:57.940
Ini pachangu ndichaona mukadzi ne kugadzirisa nyaya yacho.

0:10:57.940,0:11:03.900
Mukadzi wacho achaenda kuno nununurwa nhasi, munyengetero nhasi, uye iye achasiya imba.

0:11:03.900,0:11:09.880
Hatidi kuti vangosiya hukama mukusawirirana ne ruvengo.

0:11:09.880,0:11:16.080
Kusiya rudzi rwehukama hwakadai, nyaya yacho yese inoda kunzwisiswa ku mativi maviri ose,.

0:11:16.080,0:11:19.300
uye murume uyu anogona kupfuurira -

0:11:19.300,0:11:24.080
Ndinoziva vakawanda venyu, munozviona ne nzira yakasiyana.

0:11:24.080,0:11:30.900
Dzimwe nguva, Mwari anogona kutaura zvakanaka kuburikidza nezvakaipa.

0:11:30.900,0:11:32.140
Ndiye Mwari kwauri.

0:11:32.140,0:11:36.420
Ndinoziva vazhinji venyu, nekuda kweizvi, iwe unosiya muchato.

0:11:36.420,0:11:41.240
Wanano zhinhji - pane vanhu vakawanda pano vanosiya wanano dzavo

0:11:41.240,0:11:44.360
nekuda kwezvakaitika - zvinhu zvakadaro.

0:11:44.360,0:11:48.600
Asi nhasi, une wanano chaiyo here?

0:11:48.600,0:11:53.600
Chero chii zvacho chinoitika, chiongorore muchiedza cha Mwari.

0:11:53.600,0:11:58.880
Chinhu chipi nechipi chinoitika mumuchato wako, bvunza Mwari kuti anoti chii pamusoro pazvo.

0:11:58.880,0:12:03.360
Mumamiriro ezvinhu ose, Anoti kudii?

0:12:03.360,0:12:10.600
Mhinduro yacho haisi kusiya asi chinhu chekutanga ndechokubvunza Mwari pfungwa dzake -

0:12:10.600,0:12:14.540
chii cha Anofunga, mazano Ake pamusoro pezvakaitika -

0:12:14.540,0:12:18.600
usati wafunga nezvekusiya kana kugara.

0:12:18.600,0:12:23.560
Apo chimwe chinhu chinoitika, zvisinei kuti chikuru sei, Anoti kudii.

0:12:23.560,0:12:28.760
Mumamiriro ezvinhu ose, Mwari ane chimwe chinhu chekutaura.

0:12:28.760,0:12:31.540
Saka, hatingosiya chero chinhu -

0:12:31.540,0:12:36.460
zvingave mu wanano, ukama, hushamwari mu bhizinesi kana chero chii -

0:12:36.460,0:12:38.440
chero hukama zvaho.

0:12:38.440,0:12:39.820
Hazvina mhosva kuti chii chakaitika.

0:12:39.820,0:12:46.920
Kana Mwari akatanga kuunza ukama uhwu, ndiye Mwari mumwe chete uyo achakusunungura iwe ne kumusunungura iye,

0:12:46.920,0:12:49.620
kwete dambudziko, kwete mamiriro ezvinhu.

0:12:49.620,0:12:55.760
Hatifanirwe nekuda kwemamiriro ezvinhu kuzvisunungura pachedu kana kusiya hukama.

0:12:55.760,0:12:59.120
Hazvina mhosva mamiriro acho ezvinhu, Chii cha Anotaura

0:12:59.120,0:13:04.040
nokuti Ndiye Baba vehukama.

0:13:04.040,0:13:11.780
Kana zvisina kudaro, iwe uchasiya ukama uhwu wosangana nemumwe munhu akasiya hukama nekuda kwedambudziko.

0:13:11.780,0:13:13.380
Vaviri imi muchasangana.

0:13:13.380,0:13:15.520
Iwe wakarega hukama nekuda kwedambudziko

0:13:15.520,0:13:18.660
uye iwe unosangana nomumwe munhu akarega hukama nekuda kwedambudziko.

0:13:18.660,0:13:22.040
Vaviri venyu - matambudziko maviri achasangana.

0:13:22.040,0:13:26.720
Svondo ye musi we Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:13:26.720,0:13:34.120
Kana iwe ukasiya ukama uhwu nekuda kwematambudziko - kana kunyadziswa, kutengeswa kana chero chii zvacho -

0:13:34.120,0:13:46.040
uye iwe ukarega, uchawana kupi munhu asina kurega hukama kare nekuda kwedambudziko?

0:13:46.040,0:13:50.420
Kana iwe ukarega ukama uhwu usina kuporeswa,

0:13:50.420,0:13:54.600
iwe uchasangana nemumwe munhu akasiya hukama asina kuporeswa.

0:13:54.600,0:13:57.580
Vaviri imi muchasangana.

0:13:57.580,0:14:02.480
Nzira iyo iwe unosiya ukama uhwu ndiyo nzira yaunosangana nayo hukama hutsva.

0:14:02.480,0:14:07.500
Matambudziko mazhinji atinawo mazuva ano anokonzerwa ne hukama hwatinosiya zuva nezuva.

0:14:07.500,0:14:15.920
Mubetseri mu bhizimisi, mukuroorana, shamwari - nzira yawakasiya nayo -

0:14:15.920,0:14:18.300
iwe unongosiya ukama.

0:14:18.300,0:14:28.600
Munhu ari mupari we mhosva nhasi, anogona kuve mesiya mangwana, kana iwe ukatsungirira.

0:14:28.600,0:14:36.780
Takaona munhu waunoti akakutengesa, akakugumbura,

0:14:36.780,0:14:39.820
uye iwe unorega ne kumisiya.

0:14:39.820,0:14:48.240
Zvino iye zvino, ndiye munhu mumwe chete wauchasangana naye mune ramangwana achazomira kuve muponesi wako.

0:14:48.240,0:14:51.060
Iwe zvino unoti, "Aa!"

0:14:51.060,0:14:53.760
Ndizvo zvinoita hupenyu.

0:14:53.760,0:14:57.580
Mwari ndiye ane ramangwana redu. Iwe hauzive kuti ramangwana rakabata chii.

0:14:57.580,0:15:06.240
Zvakaipa nhasi zvinogona kuve zvakanakisisa mangwana uye zvakanakisisa nhasi zvinogona kuva zvakaipa mangwana.

0:15:06.240,0:15:09.960
Mupari we mhosva nhasi anogona kuva muponesi mangwana.

0:15:09.960,0:15:14.060
Munhu asina kutendeseka anogona kuva akavimbika mangwana.

0:15:14.060,0:15:16.940
Ndiri kureva kuti, ndizvo zvakaita hupenyu

0:15:16.940,0:15:22.320
Mushure mekuyananiswa nemhuri, Mr Emmanuel akadzoka mushure me vhiki mbiri.

0:15:22.320,0:15:26.080
kuzopupura kuti Mwari akadzikinura sei imba yake.

0:15:26.080,0:15:27.580
Ngatiteererei kwaari.

0:15:27.580,0:15:31.620
HUCHAPUPU HUNOENDERERA

0:15:31.620,0:15:35.180
Zita rangu ndi Mr Emmanuel.

0:15:35.180,0:15:36.740
Ini ndinobva kuTogo.

0:15:36.740,0:15:38.980
Mukadzi ari pedyo neni mudzimai wangu.

0:15:38.980,0:15:43.220
Ini ndakaroorana ne mu Nigeria; iye anobva ku Ebonyi State (Nigeria).

0:15:43.220,0:15:52.400
Panguva ye uporofita musi wa December 10, munhu wa Mwari akaporofita kuti kune murume

0:15:52.400,0:15:57.920
pano arikurendera umwe mukadzi wekunze imba muchivande, munhu wacho ndini.

0:15:57.920,0:16:00.080
Nhasi, tinovonga Mwari.

0:16:00.080,0:16:09.300
Mushure mezvo, munhu wa Mwari akationa, akayananisa mhuri, akati yambiro nekugadzirisa zvinhu zvose.

0:16:09.300,0:16:12.300
Zvino, ndakagamuchira mwana wangu.

0:16:12.300,0:16:18.320
Mwana wacho ndewe mudzimai wangu uye achadana mudzimai wangu kuti 'amai'.

0:16:18.320,0:16:25.580
Ndinoda kutenda munhu wa Mwari kuti akazvibvumira kushandiswa na Mwari kugadzirisa nyaya iyi.

0:16:25.580,0:16:28.280
Ndisati ndasvika pano, ndakanga ndakafanana nemurume akanga ari pedyo nekufa.

0:16:28.280,0:16:30.960
Handaikwanisa kurara. Ndakanga ndisina rugare.

0:16:30.960,0:16:35.900
Asi kubvira ipapo, ndinogona kurara; dzimwe nguva, mudzimai wangu ndiye anozondimutsa.

0:16:35.900,0:16:39.860
Kare, ndaigona kumuka kanopfuura katanhatu usiku.

0:16:39.860,0:16:44.000
Zvino, rudo rwasiyana ne rwekare.

0:16:44.000,0:16:49.160
Iye zvino, isu tiri kugara zviri nani kupfuura kare, ndinoziva kuti uku ndiko kutanga kwemuchato.

0:16:49.160,0:16:50.260
Ndatenda.

0:16:50.260,0:16:53.940
Ameni. Ngatiuchirei kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:16:53.940,0:17:00.700
Ndihwo uchapupu mushure me uporofita ne munyengetero ne munhu wa Mwari.

0:17:00.700,0:17:06.060
Mushure mekusangana nemhuri, ati hupenyu hwake hwagadziriswa zvakare.

0:17:06.060,0:17:10.840
Asati asvika pari zvino, aive asina kugadzikika, zvinhu zvose zvakanga zviri manyama amire nerongo.

0:17:10.840,0:17:12.940
Makanga musina runyararo mumwoyo make.

0:17:12.940,0:17:15.380
Asi ikozvino, mave nerunyararo.

0:17:15.380,0:17:19.840
Zivo yakarurama ya Mwari yakagadzirisa rugare mumhuri.

0:17:19.840,0:17:22.080
Saka, ngatinzwei kubva kuna madhamu.

0:17:22.080,0:17:26.700
Baba Emmanuel ne Mudzimai - Huchapupu Hwe Yanananiso

0:17:26.700,0:17:29.800
Zita rangu ndi Mai Chika.

0:17:29.800,0:17:32.960
Ini ndiri wemu Nigeria, ndakaroorana newe ku Togo.

0:17:32.960,0:17:37.120
Murume ari pedyo neni ndiye murume wangu.

0:17:37.120,0:17:42.460
Ndiri pano kutenda Mwari pamusoro pezva Akaita muupenyu hwedu

0:17:42.460,0:17:49.480
kuburikidza nomunhu wa Mwari, mu Porofita T.B. Joshua, pakudzorera imba yedu nemhuri.

0:17:49.480,0:17:51.480
Ndiri pano kutenda Mwari.

0:17:51.480,0:17:56.220
Tiri kufara; munhu wa Mwari akatigadzirisa ne kutiraira.

0:17:56.220,0:17:59.600
Tiri kufara. Tiri pano kutenda Mwari nokuda kwaizvozvo.

0:17:59.600,0:18:02.320
Ameni.

0:18:02.320,0:18:06.280
Waregererawo murume wako kubva pamwoyo wako here?

0:18:06.280,0:18:12.220
Hongu, ndakakanganwira murume wangu, uye ndagadzirira kutora mwana wacho sewangu.

0:18:12.220,0:18:17.560
Ameni. Ngatiomberei maoko edu kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:18:17.560,0:18:25.700
Handina chero chinhu chekutaura kunze kwekutenda nokuti handina kumboziva kuti zuva rakadai raizouya.

0:18:25.700,0:18:31.100
Iye zvino, ndinoda mudzimai wangu zvakanyanya kupfuura kare.

0:18:31.100,0:18:35.680
Ndakashamisika zvikuru, akabvuma mwana wacho sewake.

0:18:35.680,0:18:38.660
Ndinotenda Mwari mune zvose.

0:18:38.660,0:18:42.080
Ndinotenda Mwari we masimbaose, muzita ra Jesu.

0:18:42.080,0:18:48.680
Ndinokutendai, Jesu. Ngatiuchirirei Jesu kamwe chete zvakare!

0:18:48.680,0:18:55.160
Saka, Madhamu, maererano nenyaya iyi, mungatiudza here - makasangana nemunhu wa Mwari,

0:18:55.160,0:18:59.240
uye munhu wa Mwari kuburikidza nesimba re Mweya Mutsvene akapindira munyaya iyi -

0:18:59.240,0:19:02.420
Tisati tasvika pari zvino takaonana nemunhu wa Mwari.

0:19:02.420,0:19:07.100
Munhu wa Mwari akaprofita kwandiri kuti ndichava nemwana wangu.

0:19:07.100,0:19:12.160
Saka, ndiri kufara. Ndagadzirira kutora mwana wacho sewangu.

0:19:12.160,0:19:15.340
Ameni. Kukudzwa ngakuve kuna Mwari! Saka, manzwa izvozvo.

0:19:15.340,0:19:18.720
Munhu wa Mwari akasunungura shoko reuporofita kwaari

0:19:18.720,0:19:23.900
kuti zvino, sezvaari kugadzirira kutora mwana uyu semwana wake,

0:19:23.900,0:19:28.460
kuti Mwari kuburikidza nechiitiko ichocho achamuropafadza.

0:19:28.460,0:19:31.340
Ari kudzoka zvakare kuzopupura pamusoro pazvo.

0:19:31.340,0:19:38.080
Tinotenda kuti zvichava sekutaurwa kwazvakaitwa na Mwari, muzita ra Jesu.

0:19:38.080,0:19:43.300
Saka, izvozvi, pasina zvimwe zvekutaurazve, tinoda kukoka mukadzi -

0:19:43.300,0:19:47.460
amai vemwana - pakati pedu.

0:19:47.460,0:19:54.320
Sekutaura kwavo, Mai Chika vanobvuma norudo kutora mwana muduku semwana wake chaiye.

0:19:54.320,0:20:00.680
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwechete kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:20:00.680,0:20:08.220
Sekurairwa kwe hu Mwari kwaakaitwa nemunhu wa Mwari uye ne kuvimbisa kuti achazvita,

0:20:08.220,0:20:14.560
madhamu vatora mwana kubva kuna amai vekumubereka

0:20:14.560,0:20:19.320
uye vabvuma kutora mwana semwana wavo.

0:20:19.320,0:20:24.640
Uyu ndiye mwanakomana wangu kubva zvino, uye ndiri kufara.

0:20:24.640,0:20:30.700
Ngatiombererei Jesu!

0:20:30.700,0:20:33.640
Ndatenda. Mwari vakukomborere.

0:20:33.640,0:20:37.100
Madhamu, tinotenda Mwari Wamasimbaose nokuda kwezvose.

0:20:37.100,0:20:41.700
Tinovimba, nekukokwa pano nekuda kwe nyaya iyi

0:20:41.700,0:20:46.720
uye Mwari apindira munyaya iyi, imi munoti kudii?

0:20:46.720,0:20:49.560
Emanueri! (Mwari Anesu - Mateo 1:23)

0:20:49.560,0:20:52.220
Zita rangu ndi Miss Charity.

0:20:52.220,0:20:56.160
Ini ndinobva kuEbonyi State.

0:20:56.160,0:20:58.160
Zvakanaka

0:20:58.160,0:21:04.740
Ndinotenda Mwari nekuda kwa nhasi.

0:21:04.740,0:21:10.780
Ndiri pano kuti ndikumbire ruregerero kuna sisi vangu

0:21:10.780,0:21:14.620
nekupa mwana wacho kumhuri

0:21:14.620,0:21:21.060
kuitira kuti mudzimai achengete mwana.

0:21:21.060,0:21:22.820
Ndino tenda.

0:21:22.820,0:21:32.520
Ndinotenda zvakare munhu wa Mwari, mu Porofita T.B. Joshua, pakuzarura izvi.

0:21:32.520,0:21:34.520
Ndinotenda Mwari kwazvo.

0:21:34.520,0:21:45.220
Uyewo ndinokumbira kwaari kuti andiregerere nekukanganwa.

0:21:45.220,0:21:49.720
Zvakanaka, tanzwa zvose. Kukudzwa ngakuve kuna Mwari kumusoro soro!

0:21:49.720,0:21:56.360
Hareruya! Ngatiuchirirei Jesu Kristu!

0:21:56.360,0:22:00.400
Saka, madhamu, manzwa kubva kune hanzvadzi.

0:22:00.400,0:22:04.320
Ari kukumbira ruregerero pane zvose zvakaitika munguva yapfuura.

0:22:04.320,0:22:09.460
Isu tose tinoziva kuti vanhu vose vanoita zvikanganiso asi zvikanganiso zvinogadziriswa.

0:22:09.460,0:22:14.060
Nenyasha dza Mwari, zvikanganiso zvose zvekare zvaruramiswa nhasi,

0:22:14.060,0:22:18.060
uye sezvaataura, munoti chii kwazviri, madhamu?

0:22:18.060,0:22:23.100
Ndamuregerera.

0:22:23.100,0:22:25.000
Isai maoko enyu pamwechete kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:22:25.000,0:22:28.520
Ndakuregerera.

0:22:28.520,0:22:32.040
Ndatenda. Mwari vakukomborere.

0:22:32.040,0:22:37.820
Zvino sezvo wanano iyi yachengetedzwa,

0:22:37.820,0:22:43.500
uye Mwari Samasimba akadzorera wanano iyi,

0:22:43.500,0:22:47.440
icho chingadai chakaputsa imba yacho munguva yapfuura

0:22:47.440,0:22:49.960
Ishe Wemasimbaose akazvigadzirisa,

0:22:49.960,0:22:54.980
uye nhasi, wanano yasimbiswa, kunyange kudarika zvayaiva kare kare.

0:22:54.980,0:23:01.520
Madhamu, zvino zvamatora mutoro uyu wekuchengeta mwana uyu,

0:23:01.520,0:23:05.620
isu tinodawo kukukurudzira kuti muite izvozvo nokutendeka,

0:23:05.620,0:23:11.600
muchiziva zvakakwana kuti muri kutarisa chiso cha Mwari kune chikomborero chenyu.

0:23:11.600,0:23:17.340
Uye apo munochengeta mwana uyu, sekuraira kwe munhu wa Mwari pachake,

0:23:17.340,0:23:19.600
chikomborero ichi chichauya nokukurumidza

0:23:19.600,0:23:23.960
uye nekukurumidza muchadzoka nemwana wenyu

0:23:23.960,0:23:28.400
kuzopupurira kunaka kwa Mwari, muzita ra Jesu.

0:23:28.400,0:23:33.600
Saka, kubvira nhasi, imi mataura kuti zvino mava mai vemukomana,

0:23:33.600,0:23:40.280
uye isu tinokutendaiwo nekuteerera mazwi emunhu akazodzwa wa Mwari

